{"id": "art-286", "label": "Art. 286", "title": "Art. 286: Refuzul celebrării căsătoriei", "slug": "art-286", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_390662087\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1173\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_390662087\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 286: Refuzul\ncelebr&#259;rii c&#259;s&#259;toriei </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_486722153\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1172\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_486722153\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Ofi&#355;erul de stare civil&#259; refuz&#259; s&#259;\ncelebreze c&#259;s&#259;toria dac&#259;, pe baza verific&#259;rilor pe care\neste obligat s&#259; le efectueze, a opozi&#355;iilor primite sau a\ninforma&#355;iilor pe care le de&#355;ine, în m&#259;sura în care acestea din\nurm&#259; sunt notorii, constat&#259; c&#259; nu sunt îndeplinite\ncondi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute de lege.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1797845553\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1171\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1797845553\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cazul în care opozi&#355;ia este formulat&#259; cu\nprivire la c&#259;s&#259;toria unei persoane care beneficiaz&#259; de\nconsiliere judiciar&#259; sau tutel&#259; special&#259;, ofi&#355;erul de stare\ncivil&#259; sesizeaz&#259; de îndat&#259; instan&#355;a de tutel&#259;, care va\nhot&#259;rî cu privire la temeinicia opozi&#355;iei.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}